1
00:00:38,479 --> 00:00:40,039
Your plan really is pretty good

2
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,119
It worked great

3
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:42,920
All it took was a little money

4
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,799
to throw them into utter chaos

5
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:45,960
Yes, Father

6
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,119
I could've handled it

7
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:49,920
You don't trust me

8
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,840
so you sent people into Commoners' Alley

9
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:52,840
to stir things up?

10
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,359
That was to back you up

11
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,600
It's easy to make them fight over money

12
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:01,880
But to fix the demolition issue

13
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,719
you haven't done enough

14
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:05,560
If demolition drags on for months

15
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:07,159
we're the ones who lose money

16
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,159
But with this riot

17
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,680
they've suffered plenty

18
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,040
Public opinion has swung back to us

19
00:01:14,319 --> 00:01:15,359
Those poor bastards

20
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:17,319
will all give up resisting

21
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,439
Go to Commoners' Alley tomorrow

22
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:24,519
Say that because of the riot

23
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:26,159
they've canceled the signing bonus

24
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:27,840
Tell them

25
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,799
Either cooperate and behave

26
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,439
or else

27
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,200
wait for forced demolition

28
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,680
Yes, Father

29
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,400
If there's nothing else

30
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:37,879
I'll head back first

31
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,000
Wait

32
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,000
About this house

33
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,480
you pay for it

34
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,319
and put it under Zhang Xiaobei's name

35
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,760
What kind of deal is that?

36
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:54,920
Actually, my goal

37
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,040
lines up with yours, Father

38
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,280
It's Sowing discord

39
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,799
to make it look like the Zhangs took kickbacks

40
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,200
so everyone else thinks

41
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,599
the Zhangs started the trouble

42
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,760
to block signing deals and profit from it

43
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,719
and spark conflict among them

44
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,000
Then we get rid of the Zhangs leading it

45
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:12,680
Is that really it?

46
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,439
Yes

47
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,319
In that case

48
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,800
now that we've achieved the goal

49
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,199
this house

50
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,199
is useless now

51
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,000
Take care, Father

52
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,759
The media's already painted people in Commoners' Alley

53
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,199
as greedy rioters

54
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:41,000
Any more protests won't do a thing

55
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:42,879
Now the house is gone too

56
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,560
and we won't get demolition compensation

57
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,159
Dad and Mom will really sleep on the street

58
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,719
What am I supposed to do?

59
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,159
There's only three days left

60
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,800
I have to fix this fast

61
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:05,159
Still, thanks for finding people for me

62
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,639
for giving me a hand

63
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,280
to settle the Commoners' Alley mess

64
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,120
Here's to you. Come on

65
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,840
I thought you'd blame me

66
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,479
After all, that's your home

67
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,280
I get it

68
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:20,479
Sheng Shizhong came to you

69
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,039
You couldn't exactly refuse him

70
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,280
Didn't think you'd be so reasonable

71
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,039
Still, thank you

72
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,560
If you hadn't helped me

73
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,479
buying a house for my family

74
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,919
would've been exposed for sure

75
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,840
You were way too blatant

76
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:44,960
Weren't you afraid that old fox Sheng Shizhong

77
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,680
would suspect you?

78
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,120
Even if he's paranoid

79
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,800
he'd never imagine

80
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,000
that in this world

81
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,400
there's such a thing as switching lives

82
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,240
If I remember right

83
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,639
you've got three days left

84
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,159
Are you really going to switch back?

85
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,840
What do you think?

86
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,360
Bottoms up

87
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,120
Who were the ones stirring up trouble in Commoners' Alley?

88
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:26,160
Just some street punks, that's all

89
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,240
What are their names?

90
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,680
How would I know?

91
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,439
They're just a bunch of nobodies

92
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:33,040
Where can I find them?

93
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,199
Why are you looking for them?

94
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,120
You're not drunk

95
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,079
Of course not

96
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,480
Whatever you're trying to do

97
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,360
I'd tell you to drop it

98
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,519
You know what happens if you defy Sheng Shizhong

99
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,319
I'm sure you know that damn well

100
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,160
They're my parents

101
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,920
My family

102
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,360
I can't just abandon them

103
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,079
I understand

104
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,800
You can't watch your parents end up on the street

105
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:03,639
How about this

106
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,959
As long as you go back to being Sheng Yuanzhou

107
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:07,519
and marry me into the Sheng family

108
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:09,560
I can take care of your family for you

109
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,600
Then you won't have to worry about Sheng Shizhong

110
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,279
suspecting you

111
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,480
Well?

112
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:15,240
I'm going back, no matter what

113
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,720
Then there's nothing I can do

114
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:21,160
Think hard about what I offered you

115
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:23,160
When you come around, come find me anytime

116
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,439
What are you doing here?

117
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,959
I know you like to drink

118
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,279
and I know you need someone to drink with

119
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:42,879
Sure

120
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:44,560
Did Young Master Sheng plant something on me

121
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,480
like a hidden camera or what?

122
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,839
Now you even know what I need

123
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:49,560
Spit it out

124
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,439
What do you want from me?

125
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,480
What you're good at

126
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:52,959
Help me find someone

127
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,720
That's easy

128
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:55,800
Say it

129
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:56,959
Who am I looking for?

130
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:58,360
Commoners' Alley

131
00:05:59,079 --> 00:05:59,839
the ones who started the riot

132
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,360
Well...

133
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,000
That's a bit tricky

134
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,120
So you're scared of offending Sheng Shizhong too?

135
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,360
You want me to help you?

136
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,319
It's not impossible

137
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:17,959
But you gotta promise me one thing

138
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:19,279
Say it

139
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,800
You gotta drink with me

140
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:23,680
I'm not drinking with you

141
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:25,120
But I can drink for you

142
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,920
That Mr. Wang you're meeting tomorrow,

143
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,319
as far as I know,

144
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,959
he's a total boozehound

145
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:30,639
You...

146
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,480
Alright, you did your homework

147
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,560
But if you won't drink with me,

148
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,199
how am I supposed to know your limit?

149
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,160
How about this:

150
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,120
If you can outdrink me today,

151
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,240
I'll do you this favor

152
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:41,920
You help me once,

153
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,040
I help you once

154
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:44,959
Even. Nobody owes anybody

155
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,040
How's that?

156
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:46,879
For real?

157
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,560
It's a deal

158
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:28,439
Hey

159
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,879
Didn't see that coming

160
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:32,360
Kid, you're pretty tough

161
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,800
Guess being young really helps

162
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,639
You've got quite a tolerance

163
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,519
Yesterday you drank over a bottle alone,

164
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,480
then passed out right away

165
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:44,000
Not satisfied?

166
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,279
Alright

167
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,680
As we agreed yesterday,

168
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,360
I've already found the guy for you

169
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,720
I'll text the details to your phone in a bit

170
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,839
Don't worry

171
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,279
You did what you promised,

172
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,959
and I'll keep my promise too

173
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,720
Good. I'm holding you to that

174
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,480
Good thing I didn't actually get drunk

175
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,759
Time to get to business

176
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,319
Take care

177
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,519
Come by again when you've got time

178
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:27,120
Anyone else here dare to challenge me?

179
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,519
If you beat me,

180
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,399
I'll pay double

181
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:31,839
Double

182
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,480
I'll do it

183
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,080
You've got guts, kid

184
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:42,720
Good

185
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,279
Then big bro will grant your wish today

186
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,480
Come on

187
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,960
Why'd you call me here?

188
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,600
Commoners' Alley.

189
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:04,159
Those punks who led the trouble,

190
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,039
I found them.

191
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:08,480
The ringleader's Gao Hu.

192
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:09,600
People call him Brother Hu.

193
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:12,000
He's got three to five little thugs under him.

194
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:13,519
Then call the cops already!

195
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,399
Call the cops?

196
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:15,600
Do you have any evidence?

197
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,879
What would the police arrest them for?

198
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,600
I heard

199
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,960
that their crew

200
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,639
hangs around North Street a lot.

201
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:26,320
One of them, Skinny Monkey,

202
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,360
is really into betting on games.

203
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,120
This pool hall is where he comes most.

204
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,879
So you're saying...

205
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,679
I want you to make friends through pool,

206
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,279
and infiltrate their group.

207
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:38,639
Then police have proof to arrest them,

208
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,399
and it can also clear up

209
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,360
the truth about the Commoners' Alley riot.

210
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,159
But I can't play.

211
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,159
Then learn.

212
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,039
Pool ace Sheng Yuanzhou.

213
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,159
Sure enough.

214
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,519
Even without your memory,

215
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,240
you can still make great shots.

216
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,080
Double.

217
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,399
A bet is a bet.

218
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,879
Fine.

219
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,240
Double it is.

220
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:29,759
Brother Hu wants to see you.

221
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:34,720
Come on.

222
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,200
This is my big bro,

223
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,000
Brother Hu.

224
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,080
The ringleader's Gao Hu.

225
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,159
People call him Brother Hu.

226
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:44,679
Nice to meet you, Brother Hu.

227
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:46,840
Come.

228
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:55,399
Put it down.

229
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,679
Bro,

230
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,519
you play pretty well.

231
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,320
You're flattering me, Brother Hu.

232
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,240
So, wanna roll with me?

233
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,960
I'll set you up with people.

234
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,360
If you lose, it's on me.

235
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,600
If you win,

236
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:08,720
we split it 30-70.

237
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,639
How about it?

238
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,200
If Brother Hu says so,

239
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,519
then I'm in, for sure.

240
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:13,720
Good.

241
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,120
From today on, we're family.

242
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,120
Thanks, Brother Hu.

243
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:28,639
Brother Hu.

244
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,720
Just playing pool like this,

245
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,480
we can't make much money.

246
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:34,679
With Brother Hu, you think you won't make money?

247
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,679
We all work for the big boss.

248
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,919
Brother Hu, you're so capable,

249
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,360
so introduce me too, yeah?

250
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,320
You know Wanli Construction, right?

251
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,159
Yeah, I do.

252
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,240
Big company.

253
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,840
That riot in Commoners' Alley a couple days ago,

254
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,159
you heard about it, right?

255
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,840
We did it.

256
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,399
We did.

257
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,120
I had my bros blend in with the residents

258
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,240
and stir things up.

259
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,480
Whoever started fighting, we hit 'em.

260
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:03,879
They didn't even know who was who.

261
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,159
They thought

262
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:07,440
they were fighting their own people.

263
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,240
And then?

264
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,360
It just got more and more vicious.

265
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:12,519
So...

266
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:14,879
you guys made a lot of money, huh?

267
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,039
Not bad.

268
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,720
Per person,

269
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:19,039
eight thousand.

270
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:21,200
Eighty thousand.

271
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:23,639
Brother Hu, you're impressive.

272
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,080
Brother Hu,

273
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:28,679
I... I'm gonna hit the bathroom.

274
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:28,960
Go, go, go.

275
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,480
I'll be right back.

276
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:31,799
Come on, let's drink.

277
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,519
Young Miss

278
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:50,679
Young Miss

279
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:52,279
What are you doing here?

280
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,240
How are you two together?

281
00:12:57,159 --> 00:12:58,799
We met playing pool last time.

282
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,519
Playing pool?

283
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:01,720
I couldn't hold it in anymore.

284
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:05,960
Why are you standing there? Go after him!

285
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,720
He's from Commoners' Alley.

286
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,559
You got set up.

287
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:09,000
Hurry!

288
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,159
Let go of me!

289
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:16,679
Let's see where you think you're going!

290
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:17,240
Search him!

291
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:21,799
Boss, there's a recording.

292
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,679
So you framed me, huh?

293
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:48,480
What are you doing here?

294
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,360
Came to check on you.

295
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,960
Here to laugh at me, right?

296
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,679
Is it really that bad?

297
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:02,919
I knew it. You did it on purpose.

298
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,679
You sent me undercover to catch the thugs

299
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:05,879
And now look.

300
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,519
We didn't catch the thugs,

301
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:08,519
and I'm the only one suffering.

302
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,480
Don't say that.

303
00:14:10,879 --> 00:14:11,480
Look at this.

304
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,960
You know Wanli Construction, right?

305
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,000
A few days ago,

306
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:18,960
Commoners' Alley...

307
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,039
Where'd you get this?

308
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,000
Weren't all our phones confiscated then?

309
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,679
You know Wanli Construction, right?

310
00:14:25,399 --> 00:14:28,279
That riot in Commoners' Alley days ago,

311
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:29,799
You heard about it, right?

312
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,840
We did it.

313
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:41,080
You always have to keep a backup plan.

314
00:14:42,519 --> 00:14:43,399
You're pretty sly.

315
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:45,679
This video's already online.

316
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,039
In ten minutes,

317
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,919
it's hit over 100,000 likes.

318
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,279
I think the Commoners' Alley mess

319
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,480
will be over soon.

320
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:55,759
Uncle Sheng.

321
00:14:56,039 --> 00:14:57,519
I did it all exactly as you instructed.

322
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,799
You can't just hang me out to dry!

323
00:14:58,799 --> 00:15:00,039
Don't talk nonsense.

324
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,799
The video names Wanli Construction.

325
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:06,000
It has nothing to do with the Sheng family.

326
00:15:06,559 --> 00:15:07,080
Right?

327
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,519
Yes.

328
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:11,039
I didn't keep my people under control.

329
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,039
But Uncle Sheng...

330
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:14,879
Wanli Construction and the Sheng family

331
00:15:14,879 --> 00:15:15,919
have been in the same boat for a long time.

332
00:15:15,919 --> 00:15:17,080
You can't just sit back.

333
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,600
Otherwise it'll hurt the Sheng family too.

334
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,639
Show some humility.

335
00:15:24,879 --> 00:15:25,840
Admit your mistake.

336
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:28,159
Pay up and cover all their medical bills.

337
00:15:29,279 --> 00:15:30,919
In a while, people will forget.

338
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:32,519
Will that work?

339
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,600
People online are already calling for

340
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,840
a boycott of Wanli Construction.

341
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,039
Those people online

342
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,320
are just using this to vent.

343
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:42,720
In a couple days, something else will happen,

344
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,559
and they won't care about you anymore.

345
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:46,080
But I'm different.

346
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:47,960
What you've done for the Sheng family,

347
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,519
I remember it all.

348
00:15:53,279 --> 00:15:54,279
Thank you, Uncle Sheng.

349
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:55,440
Alright.

350
00:15:55,879 --> 00:15:58,240
Stay out of the Commoners' Alley matter for now.

351
00:15:58,559 --> 00:16:00,240
Once you marry into the Sheng family,

352
00:16:00,519 --> 00:16:01,720
we're all family.

353
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:02,919
We don't draw lines between us.

354
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,720
Prosperity Group issues a public statement:

355
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,559
that regarding Wanli Construction's actions,

356
00:16:06,559 --> 00:16:07,279
it had absolutely no knowledge,

357
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,840
and for their violent conduct,

358
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,799
it expresses strong condemnation.

359
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:11,000
It has immediately terminated

360
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,559
all cooperation with Wanli Construction.

361
00:16:13,159 --> 00:16:14,600
Chairman Sheng Shizhong stated

362
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,840
that for the victims of this Commoners' Alley

363
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,360
demolition incident,

364
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:20,080
Prosperity Group will offer extra funds.

365
00:16:20,159 --> 00:16:21,320
For the exact amount,

366
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,200
please stay tuned.

367
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:23,720
That's great!

368
00:16:24,399 --> 00:16:24,799
Son.

369
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,480
We did it.

370
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:26,840
Yeah!

371
00:16:28,639 --> 00:16:29,159
Come here, son.

372
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,120
Isn't this wonderful?

373
00:16:30,399 --> 00:16:31,679
Your mom wouldn't let me say it,

374
00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:33,559
about finding you a wife and all that.

375
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:34,200
Right?

376
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,440
What wife?

377
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,039
We're not getting married.

378
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:36,679
First, get ourselves together,

379
00:16:36,679 --> 00:16:37,919
then enjoy a few more years.

380
00:16:40,639 --> 00:16:41,399
Dad, Mom.

381
00:16:41,919 --> 00:16:42,960
I'll be back soon.

382
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,000
Where are you going?

383
00:17:15,279 --> 00:17:16,160
Zhang Xiaobei
